casebody.data:
CITIZENS AGAINST RESERVATION SHOPPING, et al., petitioners,
v.
Ryan ZINKE, Secretary of the Interior, et al. No. 16-572. Supreme Court of the United States April 3, 2017.

Motion of California State Association of Counties, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.
